<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary"/>
    <meta name="twitter:site" content="@btobastian"/>
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="bStats - Plugin Metrics made with ❤"/>
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="bStats collects data for plugin authors. It's free and easy to use!"/>
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://bstats.org/images/Twitter.jpg"/>

    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta name="description" content="bStats collects data for plugin authors. It's free and easy to use!"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <title>bStats — Open metrics for Minecraft plugin tinkerers</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/stylesheets/tailwind.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen"/>
    <link href="/stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-stone-50 text-slate-900 antialiased">

<% include ../templates/navigation.ejs %>

<main>
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-100/70 via-white to-white">
        <div class="absolute -left-20 top-10 -z-10 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe),transparent_70%)]"></div>
        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 -z-10 h-72 w-72 translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-8 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,#fde68a,transparent_65%)] opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe),transparent_55%)]"></div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-24 pt-28 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid items-start gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr,0.9fr]">
                <div class="space-y-9">
                    <span class="accent-pill bg-[color:var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe)] text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">Community metrics since 2016</span>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">Open-source stats for the plugins you ship just for fun</h1>
                    <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">bStats is the hobbyist-friendly way to see how your Bukkit, Spigot, Paper, Sponge, Bungee or Velocity plugin is doing out in the wild. No investors, no tracking pixels—just wholesome analytics for folks who love block games.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                        <a href="/getting-started" class="accent-bg inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold">
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.6" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                            Start collecting stats
                        </a>
                        <a href="/plugin-list" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-600 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5 transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:text-slate-900">
                            Browse plugin library
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 opacity-70" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.6" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/Bastian/bStats" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-dashed border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900">
                            <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.58 2 12.17c0 4.47 2.87 8.26 6.85 9.6.5.1.68-.22.68-.48 0-.24-.01-.87-.01-1.7-2.78.62-3.37-1.37-3.37-1.37-.46-1.18-1.12-1.5-1.12-1.5-.92-.64.07-.63.07-.63 1.01.07 1.54 1.06 1.54 1.06.9 1.58 2.36 1.12 2.94.86.09-.67.35-1.12.63-1.38-2.22-.26-4.56-1.14-4.56-5.05 0-1.12.39-2.04 1.03-2.76-.1-.26-.45-1.3.1-2.71 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.05a9.2 9.2 0 0 1 5 0c1.9-1.32 2.74-1.05 2.74-1.05.56 1.41.21 2.45.1 2.71.64.72 1.02 1.64 1.02 2.76 0 3.92-2.34 4.79-4.57 5.05.36.32.68.95.68 1.93 0 1.39-.01 2.5-.01 2.83 0 .27.18.59.69.48A10.2 10.2 0 0 0 22 12.17C22 6.58 17.52 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            View source
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-400">
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
                            No paywalls
                        </span>
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
                            GDPR friendly
                        </span>
                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>
                            Made by volunteers
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(37,99,235,0.12),transparent_65%)] blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-400">
                            <span>Project log</span>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500">
                                <span class="inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--accent-color,#2563eb)]"></span>
                                Real commits
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
                            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-200 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">GH</span>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Merge community pull request #842</p>
                                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Updated Paper metrics + added new placeholders.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </article>
                            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Servers pinging today</p>
                                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Total unique installs connected in the last 24h.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">148,263</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mt-4 h-20 w-full rounded-xl bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_20%,rgba(37,99,235,0.16),transparent_62%)]"></div>
                            </article>
                            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
                                <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-400">Recent shout-outs</p>
                                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                                    <li class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-xl bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2">
                                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
                                            Lily from Velocity devs forked the charts repo
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">2h ago</span>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-xl px-3 py-2">
                                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>
                                            15 servers opted into custom server icons
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">Today</span>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-xl bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2">
                                        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
                                            Johan opened an issue: “Add Fabric adapter?”
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">Yesterday</span>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-400">All numbers are anonymised aggregates. We keep personal data out of the dataset.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
            <div class="grid gap-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-900/5 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-400">Servers seen</span>
                    <span class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Hundreds of thousands</span>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Across Bukkit, Spigot, Paper, Sponge, Bungee and Velocity—bStats is the common telemetry layer.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-400">Plugin authors</span>
                    <span class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">10k+ profiles</span>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Every contributor gets their own dashboard and plugin list. No vendor lock-in.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-400">Events processed</span>
                    <span class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Millions / day</span>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Our redis-backed pipeline crunches your metrics and exposes them via JSON, embeds and charts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-slate-100/70 px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
            <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr,1.1fr] lg:items-center">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <span class="accent-pill bg-white text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">Why builders stay</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">A nerdy toolkit that doesn’t try to be a startup</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-7 text-slate-600">We focus on the things hobby developers actually need: clear charts, a tiny footprint and an API that plays nicely with GitHub workflows.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
                        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[color:var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe)] text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">1</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Drop-in metrics class</p>
                                <p>Ship a single class with your plugin or use our lightweight Gradle dependency. No dashboards to babysit.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[color:var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe)] text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">2</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Charts you can remix</p>
                                <p>Craft custom pies, line charts or advanced datasets. Export JSON and rebuild your own widgets if you feel fancy.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                            <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[color:var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe)] text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">3</span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Play nice with your community</p>
                                <p>Players can opt out. We document exactly what’s collected. You can point privacy questions to a single URL and chill.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-6 -z-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-slate-100 to-transparent blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="bg-grid-light rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-8 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10 backdrop-blur">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-dashed border-slate-200 pb-4">
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-400">Sample payload</p>
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Custom Pie Chart (Java)</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                                <span class="inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
                                Copy this
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <pre class="mt-5 overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-900 p-5 text-[13px] leading-6 text-slate-200 shadow-inner shadow-slate-900/40"><code>public final class ExamplePlugin extends JavaPlugin {
    @Override
    public void onEnable() {
        Metrics metrics = new Metrics(this, YOUR_PLUGIN_ID);

        metrics.addCustomChart(new Metrics.SimplePie("server_version", () ->
            Bukkit.getVersion()
        ));
    }
}</code></pre>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">Need a deeper dive? Check the <a href="https://github.com/bStats-dev/bStats-Metrics" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="accent-text transition hover:opacity-80">integration guide</a> or ask in <a href="https://discord.gg/qTXtXuf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="accent-text transition hover:opacity-80">Discord</a>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
            <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/10">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <span class="accent-pill text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">Community first</span>
                        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Maintained by people who publish plugins too</h2>
                        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-lg leading-7 text-slate-600">Every feature ships because someone in the community needed it. We keep a public Trello board, track issues on GitHub and hang out in Discord voice chats while debugging.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
                            Sponsored by GameHosting
                        </span>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-rose-500"></span>
                            100% open source
                        </span>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>
                            Issue triage weekly
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
                    <% const communityFaces = [
                        { name: 'Skylar', role: 'Paper maintainer', color: 'bg-sky-100 text-sky-600' },
                        { name: 'Nova', role: 'Velocity tinkerer', color: 'bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600' },
                        { name: 'Atlas', role: 'Designer + docs', color: 'bg-amber-100 text-amber-600' },
                        { name: 'Mira', role: 'Sponge plugin dev', color: 'bg-rose-100 text-rose-600' }
                    ]; %>
                    <% for (var faceIndex = 0; faceIndex < communityFaces.length; faceIndex++) { %>
                    <% var face = communityFaces[faceIndex]; %>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full font-semibold <%= face.color %>">
                                <%= face.name.charAt(0) %>
                            </span>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800"><%= face.name %></p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500"><%= face.role %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600">“bStats feels like documenting a LAN party. It’s nerdy, scrappy and surprisingly reliable.”</p>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,var(--accent-color-soft,#e0f2fe),transparent_55%)] px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -z-10 h-64 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
            <span class="accent-pill bg-white text-[color:var(--accent-color-dark,#1d4ed8)]">Ready to share your numbers?</span>
            <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Create an account, drop in the metrics class and watch the graphs light up.</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-7 text-slate-600">It takes about five minutes. The slowest part is remembering your plugin ID.</p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="/register" class="accent-bg inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold">
                    Create free account
                    <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.6" d="M12 5v14m7-7H5"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="/login" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-600 shadow-sm shadow-slate-900/5 transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:text-slate-900">
                    I already have an account
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<% include ../templates/footer.ejs %>

</body>
</html>
